window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A succubus.</p> <p>A Griffon.</p> <p>A Neko</p> <p>A Slime.</p> <p>A Nightmare.</p> <p>On their own, it sounds like a lot. And you'd be right. Calon is way over his head. Juggling the needs of his summons, against the needs of the farm, Calon has found himself in hot water.</p> <p>Carted before the Brisbane Magistrate, it's up to Calon and his lovers to prove his innocence. Thankfully, he's made enough friends, that his guilt is brought into question. Rather than face the gallows, Calon is given an opportunity.</p> <p>All he needs to do?</p> <p>Is to summon someone familiar!</p>"; 
